外就是将来跳槽，这个没办法作为参考，问了几个 HR 都说公司不承认这个</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>二是走国内的社保，参社城市上海，正常缴纳五险一金和税，但是这样的话每个月到手比前者少 1W 左右，感觉很亏（目前就是走这个形式）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>年底的时候同事找我聊，问我要不要拿美刀，我说不用了，先这样吧，因为考虑到将来跳槽方便，很多公司不承认美刀作为流水，毕竟这个东西人人都可以伪造，但是个税和社保是可以查到的</p>\n<p>现在过去两个月了，每次发工资看到扣税和社保都感觉好心疼，想法又开始动摇了，v 友们给点建议或者意见？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/35155cd9-9d10-487e-acf3-a632fb802186\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1736248757, "replies": 78, "id": 1103279}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27912, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3104, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 664401, "username": "omz", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/omz", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cf088dd4af96fb317a7c820cd3064a62?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cf088dd4af96fb317a7c820cd3064a62?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cf088dd4af96fb317a7c820cd3064a62?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1701001529, "last_modified": 1734920878}, "last_reply_by": "q447643445", "last_touched": 1736308757, "title": "苹果对自家 M 芯片到底施了什么魔法，为什么这么强？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1103173", "created": 1736226223, "deleted": 0, "content": "当初没有 M 芯片时，觉得 Intel 的 M